* {{<extracted-war-archive>/dist-tomcat/tomcat-4/jira.xml}} (including the {{tomcat-4}} directory)
* {{<extracted-war-archive>/dist-tomcat/tomcat-5/jira.xml}} (including the {{tomcat-5}} directory)

